<placeName cert="high">Oxyrhynchus</placeName>
<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="p.oxy;1;161" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">POxy1,161</xref></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Δημήτριος Ἡρακλείδῃ πατρὶ χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="2"/>οὐκ ἀκόλουθον πρᾶγμα ἐποίησας ἐνεδρεύσας τὰς τροφὰς τῶν κτηνῶν 

    <lb n="3"/>τῆς Σεναώ, ἔκπαλαι ἐπισταλεὶς δώδεκα <num value="12"/> σαργάνας χόρτου ἐκεῖ ἀποστεῖλαι 

    <lb n="4"/>καὶ μὴ πέμψας, ὡς ἐκ τούτου κινδυνεύειν τὰ κτήνη διαφθαρῆναι. τῶν 

    <lb n="5"/>οὖν κτηνῶν κακῶς ἐχόντων καὶ τῆς γῆς διὰ τοῦτο μὴ ποτιζομένης ἠπεί-

    <lb n="6"/>χθην καὶ νῦν σοι γράψαι ὅπως αὐτῆς ὥρας <subst><add place="inline">γομωθῆναι</add><del rend="corrected">γομω<del rend="erasure">σασ</del>θηναι</del></subst> ἐπιτηδείως τὰς σαργάνας 

    <lb n="7"/>ποιήσας ἀποστείλῃς. τῇ γὰρ ἀσχολίᾳ μου <sic>γαρ</sic> ἔδ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ο</unclear>ξας ἐπεγ<g type="apostrophe"/>γελᾶν. 

    <lb n="8"/>ἐρρῶσθαί σε πολλοῖς χρόνοις 

    <lb n="9"/>εὔχομαι. </ab></div><div n="meta.31327" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.31327" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="400" notBefore="276" type="textDate">spätes III - IV</date></p></div><div n="meta.31327" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">6</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">938</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">31327</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">6</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">938</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0181;6;938" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.31327" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.31327" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">P.Oxy. I 161 descr.</bibl></div><div n="meta.31327" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="de"><head lang="de">Deutsch:</head><bibl type="translations">Schubart, Ein Jahrtausend am Nil (1912) 84 und (1923) 86.</bibl></listBibl><listBibl lang="en"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl type="translations">Winter, Life and Letters (1933), S. 76</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.31327" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Oxyrhynchos</placeName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>